{"tid":1633702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由今日開始咪撚再召喚神獸","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:01.000Z","uid":124247,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d02594e875ed0ffe1ad8872ecdce1c4204ca926","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全部同我改為召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n眾所周知Batman係私了既表表者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鑒於曾經有po講過勇武唔太想叫私了，而想叫替天行道，警惡懲奸等等，同時發現私了一事令大家有唔少爭吵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹諗左好耐，不如試下改下叫法，幫件事加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">優點:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.形象正面影射:<br />\nBatman=正義既化身，警惡懲奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n係人都知，有助大眾(特別係中年同路人及淺黃)明白我地係懲罰緊d壞人，只唔係普通巿民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦都唔洗次次私了都解釋到口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />形象吻合:<br />\nBatman=黑衣+蒙面=示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">.有助外媒報導:</span>鶳了黎講係玩廣東話食字，改用Batman唔係食字，而係食佢既象徵意義，外媒易寫，國際更明我地做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有助文宣:</span>相信大家都冇乜係連儂見過私了既文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲私了既感覺係有兩方私㡳下搞掂件事既意思，冇高低對錯之說，相反用左batman之後相信要整文宣比大眾消化就易得多了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續用鶳既憂慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.神獸，獅 有猛獸既意思，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令人聯想到凶殘同暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n2.勇武曾經提及唔想大家再叫私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫召喚batman真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">百利而無一害</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然核爆都唔割，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但令人明白我地做緊咩係好重要的</span></span>，有如最近係直播加旁白師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改一少步，進一大步呀各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yszfUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yszfUo.png&h=8135f402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊跟我講一次，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1ef8b82fe5155d359b661c08daba712370b7b7eb","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a7e5a44c7720a21192eee2f9ab509e5b3867d8","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd05fcdc559ce7146f6d1f8b2b2fbd544c70c0c","tid":1633702,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，咁點撚樣先做到？<br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14ba4e01f4dbe09b87520bf3a7070d7e5967d5e","tid":1633702,"uid":114550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"其實想外國風向再轉好簡單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c52447331eaab522087ecce67a3bf9cd8c86ffd","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb67d838dcd268fd0906a17847c5b807146386ab","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b86ea6bbf46bb50e81556b1d71b58bad02d47d3","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3430e3ed67383a57587b84d7ccbaa284683d65d2","tid":1633702,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"咪撚煩啦 改個名有撚用咩 <br />\n私了就私了"},{"pid":"d901793286adb2ac528e8e735a38f669291e752f","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a563f69c11b963503d2eeb88250e61cce53bd8c4","tid":1633702,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"召喚batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0291